<div class="man pan">
    <figure class="jumbotron man pan hidden-xs hidden-sm" style="background-color: #222; height: 300px; overflow: hidden">
        <%=image_tag('welcome-banner.jpg', class: 'center-block', style: 'width:100%; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; opacity: 0.7;')%>
    </figure>
    <div class="carousel-caption mtxl hidden-xs hidden-sm">
        <p class="paxl" style="font-size: 40px">Step back and find where to start.</p>
        <%= link_to 'Try it now', {action: :new, controller: :matrices}, class: 'btn-lg btn-primary' %>

    </div>
</div>
<div class="container marketing ptl">
    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <p class="man pan text-center" style="font-size: 80px">
                <%= fa_icon('cart-plus')%>
            </p>
            <h2>Define Value</h2>
            <p class="lead">Choose a metric like $ or hours to size the <b>value</b> of your tasks.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <p class="man pan text-center" style="font-size: 80px">
                <%= fa_icon('industry')%>
            </p>
            <h2>Define Cost</h2>
            <p class="lead">Choose a metric like $ or hours to size the <b>cost</b> of your tasks.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <p class="man pan text-center" style="font-size: 80px">
                <%= fa_icon('list-ul')%>
            </p>
            <h2>List your tasks</h2>
            <p class="lead">Drop all you have in mind.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.row -->
    <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->
    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Identify traps;
                <span class="text-muted">don't work hard for no value.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lead">It is a classic error to start on something complexe and useless. Force yourself not to pick any task in the red zone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <p class="man pan text-center" style="font-size: 150px">
                <%= fa_icon('ban')%>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Do quick-wins;
                <span class="text-muted">gain confidence.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lead">You will deliver value the most productive way. You will have positive feedback, feel usefull and it will help you to keep going.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7">
            <p class="man pan text-center" style="font-size: 150px">
                <%= fa_icon('bolt')%>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Split big;
                <span class="text-muted">80/20</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lead">There is always a way to have 80% of it for 20% of the cost as M. Paretto once said.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <p class="man pan text-center" style="font-size: 150px">
                <%= fa_icon('cut')%>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading ptl pbn" align="center">
            <%= link_to 'Create a new matrix', {action: :new, controller: :matrices}, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
            <p class="ptm">
                <strong>Try it now</strong>, just click!</p>
        </div>
    </footer>


    <section class="row featurette lead">
        <h3>But when?</h3>
        <p>
            It works for every situation where you have too much on your plate; if you want an efficient way to deal with it, you just found it!
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>An easy way of getting everyone to agree on a plan?</li>
            <li>An exam tomorrow and you are 10 chapters behind?</li>
            <li>Too many books that you want to read?</li>
            <li>You want to realize a personal project?</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            The best example might be this website himself. Indeed,
            <%=link_to 'I am using this website', matrix_path('d8ff0738-9f96-4bad-82ff-ee6f95583d42') %>
            to create it.
        </p>
        <p>
            Feel free to add a task you wish to be added to Valoritization.com
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
